data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This spacious home welcomes you with a  two-story great room and an open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living spaces. The first floor master suite, is complete with an en suite bathroom featuring walk-in shower, soaker tub, his and her sinks and oversized closet. Updated kitchen showcasing granite countertops and stainless steel appliances! First floor laundry and half bathroom for convenience. The second story offers a loft and full bathroom separating the 2 bedrooms. Endless opportunities available for the unfinished full basement that includes plumbing rough-in for adding a bathroom. Step outside to the huge fenced in backyard, with irrigation system, Fire pit and beautiful patio for entertaining. Roof (2017) HVAC (2022), WH (2019) NEST/ Ring Stay!
